 Mission Data Processing software. The program will leverage the FORGE framework and BGIF for both operations and underlying hardware and software framework
 services and will continue the tasking and fusion architecture that began in Epoch 1 for Epoch 2 acquisitions. Furthermore, Epoch 2 will continue to manage a ground


