E. Acquisition Strategy
The Resilient Missile Warning and Tracking (MWT) Medium Earth Orbit (MEO) Acquisition Strategy features competition in a growing space industrial base to rapidly
field resilient capabilities at achievable technology readiness levels. This strategy combines firm fixed price contracting, other transactional authorities and consistent
industry touchpoints on iterative Middle Tier of Acquisition (MTA) pathways.




