Remarks$$, $$The HARM (High Anti-Radiation Missile) Targeting System (HTS) P3I R7 Software Update Program (SWUP) is underway to keep the HTS pod capable in a growing
threat environment. The initial SWUP 4 EMD contract awarded in July 2021 for four months with three one year options. SWUP 4 concluded in November 2025, resulting
in the final HTS software release, V 7.8802. Continuing software updates will be via contract to ensure bug fixes and ad hoc patches are developed, released, and
fielded as needed.

