Title: Controlled Reception Pattern Antenna (CRPA)/Anti-Jam Global Positioning System (GPS) Antenna                                  19.816       3.445          2.347
Description: In accordance with Capability Development Guidance Memorandum (CDGM) 09-22-03 for Resilient Position,
Navigation, and Timing (PNT), the Controlled Reception Pattern Antenna (CRPA) product line will replace the F-22's legacy Fixed
Reception Pattern Array (FRPA) antenna. CRPA/Anti-Jam Global Positioning System (GPS) Antenna provides advanced antenna
technologies which will dramatically reduce an adversary's ability to jam or otherwise interfere with GPS signals.

