Remarks
 FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE: F-15 EX is evaluated against traditional Research and Development (R&D) program expenditure benchmarks. Unlike many traditional R&D
 programs, however, the F-15 EX Development contract is a Fixed Price contract with progress payments. Twenty percent of incurred costs are withheld until the end of the
 contract, when they are liquidated. Mandatory funding obligations and progress payment withholds will cause the program to lag traditional expenditure benchmarks, painting
 an inaccurate portrait of overall program health.

