configuration that includes an ethernet switch, which allows integration of additional subsystems. Open architecture capability
would alleviate current ADCP II capacity constraints.

FY 2026 Plans:
Begin non-recurring engineering (NRE) and integration development efforts on multiple contracts to develop and integrate open
mission systems / multi-function processor (OMS/MFP) with aircraft systems to allow capability to alleviate current ADCP II
constraints.
FY 2027 Plans:
Continue non-recurring engineering (NRE) and integration development efforts on multiple contracts to develop and integrate
open mission systems / multi-function processor (OMS/MFP) with aircraft systems to allow capability to alleviate current ADCP II
constraints.
