- Continues development, demonstration, and transition for activities focused on the MTE infrastructure to provide rapid, effective
processing of key adversary SOIs and optimize data flows to provide actionable data to the warfighter
FY 2027 Plans:
- Will continue initiative development, demonstration, and transition activities focused on SOI data acquisition and conditioning
to provide MTE at scale through the identification, tracking, and engagement of numerous moving or mobile targets in a highly
contested, multi-domain environment
- Will continue development, demonstration, and transition for activities focused on enhancing Enterprise data processing
capabilities to meet tactically-relevant MTE requirements

