 0605898F, and 0605833F. In FY24 0K was expended for civilian pay expenses in this program element and in FY25 175K is forecasted for civilian pay expenses in this
 program element.

 Program is managed by Air Force Materiel Command, Agile Combat Support Directorate, Air Force Metrology Division (ROM).

Operational Systems Development

