General inflation increase
Title: Advanced Capability Development                                                                                                  3.458       3.180          3.180
Description: Provides resources to increase the Air Force SEEK EAGLE OFFICE (AFSEO) organic capabilities, to support
advanced weapons such as hypersonic weapons and other classified weapons programs, as well as investing in the development
of advanced modeling and analytical tools to make the SEEK EAGLE certification process more efficient in support of
rapid acquisition timelines. These resources include, but are not limited to: artificial intelligence, modeling and simulation
enhancements, wind tunnel model development, automated tool enhancements, information technology enhancements, and
facility improvements.

FY 2026 Plans:
-Continue to complete development of the F-35 wind tunnel model
-Continue to commence F-35 weapon certification partnership with Israeli Air Force
-Continue to support investments in other advanced modeling and simulation, automated tool, and information technology
enhancements
FY 2027 Plans:
Required resources to support fielding of advanced weapons as well as investing in the development of advanced modeling and
analytical tools to ensure the Air Force SEEK EAGLE office certification process is more efficient in support of rapid acquisition
timelines.
